{
  "texts": [
    "Subsequently, these extracted features are forwarded to the MDLSTM, which further captures high-level features and handles the classification task.",
    "The proposed hybrid approach achieved a recognition accuracy of 98.12% on the UPTI dataset [67].",
    "Transfer learningTransfer Learning (TL) offers an effective response to data scarcity [68,69] by leveraging pre-trained models from related tasks, reducing training time and the need to build models from scratch.",
    "Recently, the number of works using TL in AHR has started to grow.",
    "Researchers in this field have utilized pre-trained CNN models, often trained on extensive datasets like ImageNet, as a starting point, then fine-tuned the models on Arabic handwriting databases.Boufenar et al. [64] attempted to study the effect of TL in the context of AHCR."
  ]
}